@Node History "History..."

V1.0    » (02.07.95) First Aminet release
	- 333 game pokes are included
V1.1    - "horace goes skiing" did not have a link mark
	- 2 identified pokes
V1.2    » (06.07.95) Second Aminet release
	- 357 game pokes are included
V1.3    - Added some game hints where known.
	- 369 game pokes are included
	- Forgot to make Karnov to a link
V2.0    - Changed 'infinite' to 'unlimited' :-)
	- Much more shortcuts
	- Added alphabet at the right side
	- 647 game pokes are included

@EndNode
@Node Shortcut "Declaration of all shortcuts"

These are all shortcuts i used in this guide, and their explanation:

  BF - bug fix              removes some bugs
  EG - easy game            removes some difficulties etc.
  IM - immunity             immunity against shots, enemies etc.
  ML - maximum lives        your lives are still limited (normally 255)
  MP - multi-poke           does many good things... :-)
  NC - no collision         you cannot collide with enemies
  NE - no enemies           you're alone in this game... :)
  NS - no sound             useful late at night's
  UC - unlimited credits    you have unlimited credits
  UD - unlimited deflector  your shields are eternal
  UE - unlimited energy     you won't lose any energy
  UF - unlimited fuel       no fuel problems
  UL - unlimited lives      you have thousands of lives
  UM - unlimited money      you are rich :-)
  UO - unlimited oxygen     enough of air to breathe
  US - unlimited shots      rockets, grenades or whatsoever...
  UT - unlimited time       you have enough time to finish

  -> - link to a sublist    here you can select different pokes
  ?> - link to some hints   no pokes but useful anyway...

 "  "- function not known   i don't know what this POKE does... if
			    YOU know, please tell me!


All pokes that are marked with an asterisk '*' are tested. If this poke
does not work with your game, you do probably have a newer/older version.
Please write me, and I'll try to include another poke which might work.

@EndNode
